            <li style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">When you’re ready to connect your services, open the attached activation guide which contains your plan QR code and activation instructions. The activation process should take no longer than 10 minutes to complete.</li>
            <li style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">Moving from another provider? After you activate, call us on {{brand.support.phone}} and we’ll help you bring your existing numbers to {{brand.displayName}}.</li>
          </ol>
        </td>
      </tr>
